# Course Hub - Environment Configuration

# ===============================
# Netlify Configuration (Optional)
# ===============================

# Netlify Function URL for Trading Board (optional)
# If not set, the app will use local storage for trades
VITE_NETLIFY_FUNCTION_URL=https://your-site.netlify.app/.netlify/functions

# Database URL (for Netlify Functions with Neon PostgreSQL - optional)
# Only needed if using Netlify Functions for backend
DATABASE_URL=your_neon_database_url_here

# ===============================
# Development Notes
# ===============================

# This application works entirely in the browser with localStorage.
# All features are optional:
# - Trade board works with or without Netlify Functions
# - Uses local browser storage by default
# - Courses and schedules are stored locally
# - No external services required for basic functionality
